###Product backlog

Here’s a list of **user stories** for a product backlog of a small **fintech wallet application**:  

---

### **Core Features**  
1. **As a user, I want to create an account using my email and phone number so that I can start using the wallet.**  
2. **As a user, I want to log in securely using a password or biometric authentication so that my account remains protected.**  
3. **As a user, I want to view my wallet balance on the home screen so that I know how much money I have.**  
4. **As a user, I want to add funds to my wallet using a bank transfer or credit card so that I can use the wallet for payments.**  
5. **As a user, I want to transfer money to another user by entering their phone number or email so that I can send money easily.**  
6. **As a user, I want to request money from another user so that I can receive payments seamlessly.**  
7. **As a user, I want to view my transaction history so that I can keep track of my spending and income.**  

---

### **Security and Compliance**  
8. **As a user, I want to enable two-factor authentication (2FA) so that my account is more secure.**  
9. **As a user, I want to verify my identity by uploading an ID document so that I can comply with regulations.**  
10. **As a user, I want to receive real-time notifications for all transactions so that I am immediately aware of any activity in my wallet.**  

---

### **Payment Features**  
11. **As a user, I want to scan a QR code to make payments to merchants so that I can pay quickly and easily.**  
12. **As a user, I want to split a bill with friends by sharing the amount equally or unequally so that I can settle group expenses.**  
13. **As a user, I want to set up recurring payments for subscriptions or bills so that I don’t miss due dates.**  

---

### **Savings and Budgeting Features**  
14. **As a user, I want to set up a savings goal so that I can allocate funds toward specific objectives.**  
15. **As a user, I want to view spending analytics and categorization so that I can manage my budget effectively.**  

---

### **Rewards and Loyalty**  
16. **As a user, I want to earn cashback or rewards for certain transactions so that I feel incentivized to use the app.**  
17. **As a user, I want to redeem rewards or cashback directly into my wallet balance so that I can use them easily.**  

---

### **Customer Support**  
18. **As a user, I want to access in-app customer support via chat so that I can resolve issues quickly.**  
19. **As a user, I want to report a suspicious transaction so that I can prevent fraud or misuse of my account.**  

---

### **Advanced Features (Optional)**  
20. **As a user, I want to link my wallet to third-party apps for seamless integration with other financial tools.**  
21. **As a user, I want to invest directly through the app in preselected financial products so that I can grow my savings.**  
22. **As a user, I want to withdraw money from my wallet to my linked bank account so that I can access my funds offline.**  

---

### **Admin/User Management**  
23. **As an admin, I want to manage user accounts so that I can resolve issues and enforce compliance.**  
24. **As an admin, I want to monitor transaction patterns to identify fraudulent or suspicious activities.**  
25. **As an admin, I want to configure transaction limits and fees so that the app adheres to business rules.**  

---

This backlog provides a comprehensive starting point, with the flexibility to prioritize stories based on the minimum viable product (MVP) requirements and user needs.
